Rules.InvariantScript:
If( App.ActiveScreen in ThisItem.ChildScreens,
"data:image/svg+xml;utf8, " & EncodeUrl("<svg  xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
  <rect x='0' width='"& Self.Width &"' height='"& Self.Height &"px' rx='3' fill='rgba(116, 39, 116,1)' />
</svg>"), "")

ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString: If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(280, Self.Width - 60), Min(280, Self.Height - 60))
